================================================================================
SERVICE CARDS TEXT VISIBILITY FIX
================================================================================

Problem:
- "Network Installations" and "POS Systems" cards had text-gray-300 for subtitles
- "Laptop/Desktop/Office equipment" card had text-gray-600 for subtitle
- This caused inconsistent visibility (gray-300 is too light)

Solution:
- Changed all service card subtitles to text-gray-600
- Now all three cards have consistent, readable text

Service Cards:
1. Laptop/Desktop/Office equipment
   - Subtitle: "Professional installation and setup" (text-gray-600)
   
2. Network Installations
   - Subtitle: "Complete infrastructure setup" (text-gray-600 - FIXED)
   
3. POS Systems
   - Subtitle: "Installation and configuration" (text-gray-600 - FIXED)

================================================================================
HEADER TRANSPARENCY REMOVAL
================================================================================

Problem:
- Header had bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md (95% opacity)
- When scrolling, content behind header was visible
- This caused logo backgrounds to appear different due to transparency

Solution:
- Changed header background to bg-white (100% opaque)
- Removed backdrop-blur-md effect
- Header is now fully opaque, preventing any content bleed-through

Header Styling:
- Background: bg-white (fully opaque)
- Border: border-b-2 border-neon-cyan/20
- Position: sticky top-0 z-50
- Shadow: shadow-sm

