================================================================================

HeroCarousel Component:
- Slides: 3 slides (Laptop/Desktop, Network Installations, POS Systems)
- Auto-rotate: Every 5 seconds
- Navigation: Dot indicators at bottom (no arrows)
- Badge: Right side, top area, static, smaller size
- Badge alignment: Matches header email/phone container structure

